{"tid":995253,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[求跟進呢單野] 屯門 友愛邨 鬼故《秋天不回來》","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T11:24:22.000Z","uid":65429,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"87ee6a21332c4427bf64fffb830b34442a1a5330","tid":995253,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱SEARCH到連登1年前既POST,覺得呢單野幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但原POST得幾個回應冇後續,所以想分享多一次出黎俾各位CHING討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想睇原樓主再補充下呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我沒有女朋友<br />\n8 個月前<br />\n是咁的～<br />\n好多人都知友愛邨係屯門猛鬼既地方之一，因為經常有人係友愛邨跳樓，而最出名跳樓事件就係紅衣女鬼。但我今日講既故事唔係紅衣女鬼，而係秋天不回來既故事。話說十五年前既今日，小弟我仲係三歲小朋友咩都唔識，呢個故事都係聽我阿哥講。當年我隔離住咗一家三口，爸爸媽媽仲有粒仔，住係愛X樓17樓，個仔個陣好似已經十八歲。<br />\n<br />\n秋天既某一日，佢帶咗一個叫阿妍既女仔返屋企，佢父母睇得出佢好鍾意呢個女仔，所以無反對佢地一齊。但好竟不常，突然個女仔無啦啦消失左咁，電話唔通，短訊唔覆，個男仔梗係好傷心，仲特登上個女仔屋企搵佢，發現個女仔已經搬走。第二年既秋天，男仔透過朋友既朋友口中得知，個女仔已經識到第二男仔仲計劃結婚。就係當日既凌晨時份，個男仔上左去十八樓後樓梯，係防煙門寫咗d野就跳左落街。<br />\n<br />\n後來每日凌晨時份，隔離鄰舍就會聽到好淒怨既男聲講：秋天不回來.......秋天不回來，又有用Marker寫野既聲。為左令事件平息，街坊們就係個男仔死忌又燒衣，又拜祭，希望令男仔安息。所以愛X樓十八樓既後樓梯被燒衣既煙熏到黑曬，至今對防煙門仍然存在。房屋處無諗過換左對門，同埋重新油過後樓梯既牆身同天花板。所以有時壞lift，我會搭到十六樓行返上去，唔會搭到十八樓行返落去，因為真係好乸恐怖，屌你老母～～～～<br />\n<br />\n附上圖片兩張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/182057_485919048464db0d4de152e2d41463b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F182057_485919048464db0d4de152e2d41463b0.png&h=85d3f197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/182058_b4ad05cc514a6252274ed91079c87e83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F182058_b4ad05cc514a6252274ed91079c87e83.png&h=1f427cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原PO LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/656521/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/656521/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8e521077a582bf30fca0b989a6490bb0c946d563","tid":995253,"uid":36048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20016a657c5e5bab1281c3bbe12450e91c176528","tid":995253,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31260de93795d2881bf03e574040a7723af1f339","tid":995253,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"劉明跟進"},{"pid":"ce546176614315021bee26cbd4594ffabfd3ebd6","tid":995253,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6340fb8095894c9ce4430e239c811af1725af61","tid":995253,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"198e56e392618770008e460950608309e84d8e29","tid":995253,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717fb0d8c8eac607eb0f8cc9cf5c94bba8fcbcb9","tid":995253,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76a93788dd3b7f8abc537641c25605dddfac1160","tid":995253,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"屯門差唔多座座都有人跳過樓啦"},{"pid":"099788e1181bcc5c17ad354c152b2027096fe783","tid":995253,"uid":185142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76a93788dd3b7f8abc537641c25605dddfac1160","tid